.TH man 3 "21 October 2022" "0.01" "_printf man page"
.SH NAME
.B _print
- A simple recreation of the printf function
.SH SYNOPSYS
To use thsi function the #include "holberton.h is needed.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The _printf() function produces according to a described format
given below.
This function writes its output to the stdout, the standard output stream.
.SH USAGE
to use _print you have to use the following key characters which must be preceeded by % symbol.
.RS 3
%c: to print characters
.RS 0
%s: to print a string or strings
.RS 0
%b: To print a number in binary form
.SH RETURN VALUES
The _printf() function returns an integer representing the number of symbols
printed not couunting\\o for the string.
.SH SE ALSO
.I print(3)
